                <h1>The Origin of the Lululemon Name Explained</h1>
                <p>Lululemon's name is derived from the unique combination of "Lulu," a playful reference used by several founders, and "lemon," which evokes freshness, energy, and vitality. Founded in Vancouver in 1998, the brand originally focused on yoga apparel, blending style with function, thus embodying a vibrant, active lifestyle.</p>
